    • resolveIndicator

      public String resolveIndicator(Indicator indicatorDefinition, String indicator)
      Returns the label of the indicator if it can be found in the definition. Otherwise, returns the indicator code used.
      Parameters:
      indicatorDefinition - The definition of the indicator.
      indicator - The indicator code.
      Returns:
      The label or the indicator code depending on the existence of the indicator in the definition.
